id: pm-8d00
title: "Add MCP pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health integration tests"
description: "The MCP integration test suite (tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts, mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts) has solid coverage of pm_run, pm_search, pm_create, and pm_update. However pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, and pm_health have minimal or no MCP-specific integration test coverage. These are the highest-value MCP tools for agents: pm_context is the primary orientation tool, pm_plan drives structured agent work, pm_contracts is the machine-readable SDK surface, and pm_health is the self-repair entry point."
type: Chore
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[4]: "area:tests",coverage,integration,mcp
created_at: "2026-06-07T10:05:57.474Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-09T21:21:20.542Z"
assignee: codex-active-pm-cycle-20260609
author: audit-docs-tests-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- At least one integration test per tool (pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health) that:\n- calls the tool via the MCP handshake test harness\n- validates the compact-by-default output projection\n- validates key response shape (e.g. pm_context returns item array; pm_health returns ok boolean)"
parent: pm-u9d0
risk: medium
confidence: high
comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-09T21:06:14.019Z",codex-active-pm-cycle-20260609,"Implemented MCP integration coverage expansion: pm_context now asserts brief-by-default + depth override behavior, pm_plan asserts compact show output and deep expansion of plan.steps, pm_contracts asserts flags-only compact projection for command-scoped contracts, and pm_health compact summary coverage remains validated in mcp-handshake. Targeted MCP integration suite passed (2 files, 32 tests)."
  "2026-06-09T21:11:17.542Z",codex-active-pm-cycle-20260609,"Final verification after MCP coverage changes: pnpm build, pnpm typecheck, pnpm contracts:check, pnpm quality:static, pnpm quality:docs-links, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level low, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (149 files, 2626 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines), pnpm changelog:pm:check, pm health --check-only --summary (ok=true), and pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift (history_drift ok; known legacy 116 closed-item resolution warnings remain pre-existing)."
  "2026-06-09T21:21:20.542Z",codex-active-pm-cycle-20260609,"Applied CodeRabbit nitpick follow-up: extracted duplicated pm_context brief/deep projection assertions into tests/helpers/mcp-context-depth.ts and reused helper from both mcp-handshake and mcp-dynamic-package-actions specs. Re-ran targeted MCP integration suite (2 files, 32 tests) successfully."
