body: "## Context\nGrepped tests/integration/ for pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health:\n- pm_context: only 1 hit, in test-all-command.spec.ts (pm_context_mode metadata, not the tool itself)\n- pm_contracts: 0 dedicated MCP test hits in integration/\n- pm_plan: 0 MCP integration test hits\n- pm_health: 0 MCP integration test hits\n\nAll four tools are registered in src/mcp/server.ts but their MCP dispatch paths are not integration-tested.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- At least one integration test per tool (pm_context, pm_contracts, pm_plan, pm_health) that:\n  - calls the tool via the MCP handshake test harness\n  - validates the compact-by-default output projection\n  - validates key response shape (e.g. pm_context returns item array; pm_health returns ok boolean)\n\n## Evidence\ntests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts; tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts; grep results for pm_context/pm_contracts/pm_plan/pm_health in tests/"
